findings.title: Potential unauthorized script upgrade
findings.description: The smart contract allows potential unauthorized script upgrades due to the presence of certain functions.
findings.function: setNumTokensSellToAddLiquidity, setBuybackUpperLimit, setMarketingAddress, setSwapAndLiquifyEnabled, setBuyBackEnabled, prepareForPreSale, afterPreSale, transferToAddressETH

findings.title: Minting of unlimited number of sundae tokens
findings.description: The _mint function allows minting an unlimited number of sundae tokens without any restriction or cap.
